<plot>On February 9th, the best and the brightest will gather on one stage, during the BET Honors Award Show, to pay homage to the trailblazers and innovators in the fields of media, politics, education and more. Beyond Recognition will gather a unique blend of familiar Black American entertainment voices, to share their reflections on what is was like to participate in that wondrous evening of tribute.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?067565</url></doc>
